<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sob-v">sob <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sɒb/    美 /sɑːb/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>抽泣 (着说)；呜咽 (着说)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I sobbed bitterly, tasting the salt from the tears that streamed down my face.
我伤心地啜泣着，泪水顺着脸颊流了下来，有点咸咸的味道。</p><footer>2010 山东</footer></div></div>